snippet.textDisplay: Everything is so beautiful about this song. The singers, the classical dancer, costumes, the place and decor full of colours, and all the other performers. Authentic yet contemporary. There is true harmony across all that makes the video. Although the lyrics are provided in English, I still think the meanings in the language of the song are more beautiful. I wish to know the exact meaning of the lyrics. The vibe of the song is amazing. I feel like dancing with joy mixed with love, sadness and hope. That all said, nothing can describe how beautiful this song is.
